Clone Github Project:
https://github.com/DimitriosGkiokmema/CSC309-A2.git

Install Dependencies:
cd backend
npm install
npx prisma generate
cd ../frontend/react-app
npm install

Create ENV Files
FRONTEND .env -> place in backend directory
VITE_IMAGEKIT_PUBLIC_KEY ='public_Ezy+fEYaGELwaZbrca1PEAsLYH8='
VITE_IMAGEKIT_ENDPOINT='https://ik.imagekit.io/dimi/309_Project'
VITE_BACKEND_URL='http://localhost:3000'

BACKEND .env -> place in react-app directory
JWT_SECRET='N8e3KYm41Q9bYFOpLSEkKlyk1EsDBURPJ72edLgsuFv'
